Description:
6+ Magicians to play; 
6+ Unique magic wands; 
4+ Beautiful fighting arenas; 
Only 10 seconds to decide! 

Rock Paper Scissors game in magical style available on your device. Get into the fantasy arena, fight with mighty sorcerers, wizards and magicians in RPS battles! 

EASY RPS BATTLES 
- Choose a magician and a mighty spell; 
- Draw the sign of spell on the screen to cast; 
- Beat the opponent twice to win a furious battle; 
- Earn points to unlock new characters and magic wands! 

DEFEAT YOUR ENEMIES BY 
- Fireballs or sunbeam; 
- Lightning or stone rain; 
- Ice freezing or poisonous curse! 

VERY SMALL SIZE OF THE APP WITH 
- Simple and easy to understand user interface; 
- Amazing graphics with a unique style of magical effects! 

Good luck in the very interesting and a fun to play the game - have a pleasant time!

Hero Masters is a battler taking place on an infinite number of planets and darkest dungeons. Collect and equip a perfect combo of fantasy heroes and unleash their magic powers by drawing symbols on the screen of the device to easily crush rivals, defeat universal evil and reach the shores of a perfect world full of treasures.
Fame and glory are waiting for those who complete the quest.

FEATURES

-Dive into fun and exciting gameplay, wrapped in a cartoon style fantasy universe;
-Collect and unleash magic powers of 50 mighty heroes;
-Summon powerful spells to help you in a battle, by drawing symbols on the screen of the device;
-Defend fantasy world of tiny planets;
-Play offline on the go; 
-Compete in PvP arenas with other Masters.

Hero Masters is free to download and play, however some game items can also be purchased for real money.

